                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7779" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0210</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1019 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“惠民保”方兴未艾：人保财险的惠民之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Benefit the People Insurance&quot; is in the ascendent-PICC property insurance benefits the people&#39;s road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘德红，高若彤，袁沐曦，袁江磊，栗婧淼，靳馥境</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国人民财产保险股份有限公司湖南省分公司长沙健康保险服务中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">惠民保；人保财险；企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">benefit the people Insurance, PICC property insurance，corporate social responsibility,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例介绍了长沙人保财险为响应国家提出的深化医疗保障制度改革的号召而推出的“长沙惠民保”产品。通过介绍长沙人保财险推出“长沙惠民保”的背景、设计过程、运行模式以及理赔情况，说明“长沙惠民保”项目作为普惠性医疗保险，有利于建设多层次医疗保障体系，为低收入家庭和困难群体提供了医疗保障。尤其是“长沙惠民保”特药可保、既往症可保和重大疾病可保三大特点以及低保费、高赔付的惠民性质深受好评。长沙人保财险为“长沙惠民保”的推出做了很多努力，例如服务平台的搭建，反馈机制、投诉渠道的完善，并且通过宣传方式的多元化增加投保率和普惠力度，体现了长沙人保财险积极履行社会责任，利用自身优势，发挥央企担当。通过本案例的学习，可以加深学生对企业社会责任的理解，对保险公司发售政策性保险的社会性和商业性意义进行批判性思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case introduces the &quot;Changsha Benefit Insurance&quot; product launched by Changsha PICC in response to the state&#39;s call for deeper reform of the medical insurance system. By introducing the background, design process, operation mode and claims settlement of &quot;Changsha Benefit Insurance&quot;, the case illustrates that &quot;Changsha Benefit Insurance&quot;, as a universal medical insurance, is conducive to the construction of a multi-level medical insurance system and provides medical protection for low-income families and the needy. It provides medical protection for low-income families and groups in need. In particular, the three features of &quot;Changsha Benefit Insurance&quot;, i.e. coverage for special drugs, coverage for past illnesses and coverage for major diseases, as well as its low premiums and high benefits, were well received by the public. Changsha PICC has made a lot of efforts for the launch of &quot;Changsha Benefit Insurance&quot;, such as building the service platform, improving the feedback mechanism and complaint channels, and increasing the coverage rate and benefits through diversified publicity methods, which reflects that Changsha PICC is actively fulfilling its social responsibility and taking advantage of its own advantages to play the role of a central enterprise. This case study will deepen students&#39; understanding of corporate social responsibility and allow them to think critically about the social and commercial significance of insurance companies offering policy-based insurance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《MBA商业伦理与社会责任》、《伦理道德与社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；公私合作治理理论；风险分担理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
